title: Charges dropped against three men accused of raping 14yo in Geelong - ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation)
text:
Charges dropped against three men accused of raping 14yo in Geelong Posted February 24, 2017 11:29:41 
Charges have been dropped against three men who were accused of raping a 14-year-old girl in Geelong in 2015. 
More to come.
